<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">David Mamet</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:David_Mamet_2_by_David_Shankbone.JPG" class="image" title="David Mamet 2 by David Shankbone.JPG"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/David_Mamet_2_by_David_Shankbone.JPG/200px-David_Mamet_2_by_David_Shankbone.JPG" width="200" height="309" border="0" /></a><br />
